    <h1>Volunteer Quiz</h1>
    <p>Find out what volunteering best suits you in the Wake County area
    <form action="/results" method="post">
      
      <h2>What do you like to do in your freetime?</h2>
      <input type="radio" name="option" value="4">Cooking 
      <input type="radio" name="option" value="2">Walk my dog
      <input type="radio" name="option" value="3">Hang out with friends
      <input type="radio" name="option" value="1">Play sports
      <br>
      <div></div>
      <h2>Do you know how to cook?</h2>
      <input type="radio" name="cook" value="4">Yes
      <input type="radio" name="cook" value="2">No
      <br>
      <div></div>
      <h2>Would you rather do something more active or more sedintary?</h2>
      <input type="radio" name="sports" value="2">Active
      <input type="radio" name="sports" value="4">Sedintary
      <br>
      <div></div>
      <h2>Do you enjoy indoor or outdoor events more?</h2>
      <input type="radio" name="inorout" value="4">Indoor
      <input type="radio" name="inorout" value="2">Outdoor
      <br>
      <div></div>
      <h2>Do you like kids?</h2>
      <input type="radio" name="kids" value="2">Yes
      <input type="radio" name="kids" value="4">No
      <br>
      <div>
      <button type="submit" class="new">Submit</button>
